<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media -- Advertising:
   Tatham's Beers Resigns, Sparking
   Specualtion Over Her Next Move
   ----
   By Joanne Lipman
</HL>
<DATE>
02/24/92
</DATE>
<SO>
